videos.headline: Travis Dye opens Oregon's scoring with 20-yard rushing TD
videos.description: Oregon's Travis Dye takes the run up the middle for a 20-yard Ducks touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Travis Dye opens up scoring with 20-yard rushing TD) 11/27/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon goes over the top for 50-yard TD
videos.description: Anthony Brown connects with Devon Williams to put the Ducks up 14-0.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Oregon goes over the top for 50-yard TD) 11/27/21 ESHEET

videos.description: Anthony Brown keeps it and lunges the ball over the goal line for an Oregon touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Anthony Brown crosses the plane by a hair for an Oregon TD) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.description: Oregon gets the interception to end the half

videos.headline: Musgrave gets Oregon State back in game with 4th-down TD
videos.description: Chance Nolan finds tight end Luke Musgrave for the Oregon State touchdown, getting the Beavers back in the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Musgrave gets Oregon State back in game with 4th-down TD) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brown rips pass to Hutson for Oregon TD
videos.description: Anthony Brown ropes a pass to Kris Hutson, who outmuscles the defender for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brown rips pass to Hutson for Oregon TD) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: B.J. Baylor breaks the plane for Oregon State TD

videos.headline: Oregon State recovers onside kick, then scores TD

videos.headline: Cardwell's big run sets up Oregon TD
videos.description: Byron Cardwell gets Oregon to the 1-yard line, leading to Travis Dye scoring the short touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cardwell's big run sets up Oregon TD) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fight breaks out between Oregon State, Oregon
videos.description: Oregon State scores the touchdown, but after the play multiple players exchange punches.

videos.headline: Anthony Brown's 3 TDs lead Oregon to the win over rival Oregon State
videos.description: Anthony Brown throws two touchdowns and runs for one, leading the Ducks to the win over the rival Beavers.
